%F A220779 a(n) = d - 1 or 2*(d - 1), according as n or n+1 = 2^d * odd, with d > 0.
%F A220779 a(n) = A007814(A031971(n)).
%e A220779 1^3 + 2^3 + 3^3 = 1 + 8 + 27 = 36 = 2^2 * 9, so a(3) = 2.
